    "To reduce random factors and ensure an exhaustive evaluation, we run each question with every jailbreak prompt for 10 rounds, accumulating to a total of 68,000 queries (5 questions × 4 prohibited scenarios × 85TABLE II: Number and ratio of successful jailbreaking attempts for different models and scenarios.",
